 Finally, he discusses the high 
\begin_inset Formula $Z$
\end_inset

 techniques, which all leverage the attenuation of 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma$
\end_inset

s inside of SNM.
 He lays out a table describing the properties of each technique in a table.
\end_layout

